1
00:01:30,220 --> 00:01:32,980
Episode 20

2
00:01:36,400 --> 00:01:37,000
President Yan.

3
00:01:38,280 --> 00:01:39,480
Send Mr. Tong away?

4
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:41,400
What did he say?

5
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:42,310
He...

6
00:01:45,430 --> 00:01:46,350
My fault.

7
00:01:47,070 --> 00:01:48,120
I've caused a great loss

8
00:01:48,150 --> 00:01:48,950
to the company.

9
00:01:49,950 --> 00:01:51,230
I'll take the responsibility.

10
00:01:58,150 --> 00:01:59,480
You're not familiar with

11
00:02:00,150 --> 00:02:01,400
the business line.

12
00:02:01,680 --> 00:02:03,560
Only calculated profits

13
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:04,840
but failed to pay attention

14
00:02:04,840 --> 00:02:06,590
to the raw material prices.

15
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:08,240
You did overstep your authority,

16
00:02:09,150 --> 00:02:10,080
but you're not reckless.

17
00:02:19,470 --> 00:02:21,280
For my stupidity and recklessness,

18
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:22,280
I need to say sorry.

19
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,840
I'll accept dismissing me.

20
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:28,470
I've checked your mail to President Yan.

21
00:02:29,310 --> 00:02:31,430
The opponent was too cunning.

22
00:02:32,190 --> 00:02:32,710
Of course,

23
00:02:32,910 --> 00:02:33,520
in the management,

24
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:34,430
we still have flaws.

25
00:02:38,120 --> 00:02:39,150
As for dismissal,

26
00:02:39,590 --> 00:02:40,910
that was the heat of the moment.

27
00:02:41,630 --> 00:02:42,870
Although you're a novice,

28
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:44,030
you're responsible

29
00:02:44,030 --> 00:02:44,870
and considerate.

30
00:02:45,430 --> 00:02:46,520
Hongtu and President Yan

31
00:02:46,710 --> 00:02:48,680
are willing to give you a new chance.

32
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:21,800
Fang Wanzhi...

33
00:03:24,910 --> 00:03:25,710
Again...

34
00:03:58,800 --> 00:03:59,430
Auntie Wanzhi.

35
00:03:59,630 --> 00:04:00,680
Your phone has been ringing.

36
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:01,800
I was about to send it to you.

37
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:06,470
Hello, Mr. Yan.

38
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:08,630
Now?

39
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:11,800
Okay.

40
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:14,400
I'll go out for a bit.

41
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:15,630
This late?

42
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:17,510
Don't tell me your president want you

43
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:18,800
to have a drink with him.

44
00:04:19,190 --> 00:04:20,000
I don't know.

45
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:21,430
I'll head out.

46
00:04:21,870 --> 00:04:22,630
Be careful.

47
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:23,480
Take it easy.

48
00:04:40,070 --> 00:04:40,720
Mr. Yan.

49
00:04:41,830 --> 00:04:42,750
What can I do for you?

50
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:43,830
I'll prepare it now.

51
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:45,000
Just sit.

52
00:04:46,310 --> 00:04:47,430
I ordered coffee for you.

53
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:50,270
It's hot.

54
00:04:50,950 --> 00:04:51,480
Thank you.

55
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:53,750
I've checked your email.

56
00:04:54,310 --> 00:04:55,830
Your suggestion for

57
00:04:55,950 --> 00:04:57,310
Hongtu's future business

58
00:04:57,870 --> 00:04:59,830
and the high-tech fair

59
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:01,510
impressed me.

60
00:05:02,190 --> 00:05:03,800
So I want to know

61
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:05,510
more details in person.

62
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:07,560
I'm so sorry

63
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:09,160
for sparing your private time.

64
00:05:09,390 --> 00:05:10,040
No.

65
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:11,430
It's me who wants

66
00:05:11,510 --> 00:05:12,680
to do that.

67
00:05:13,630 --> 00:05:15,190
If I give you a chance

68
00:05:16,190 --> 00:05:17,680
to persuade the management,

69
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:19,390
what will you say?

70
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:22,680
Don't be nervous.

71
00:05:22,830 --> 00:05:24,390
Just treat me as one of them

72
00:05:24,750 --> 00:05:26,360
and tell me your thoughts.

73
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:27,560
You can start it now.

74
00:05:33,430 --> 00:05:34,680
Well, as I think,

75
00:05:34,950 --> 00:05:37,630
Hongtu is technology-focused.

76
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:38,680
The high-tech fair

77
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:40,920
happens to magnify our advantages.

78
00:05:41,870 --> 00:05:43,310
I'll talk about it from two sides.

79
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:45,390
First, in the short term, we can gain...

80
00:06:17,510 --> 00:06:18,510
Okay, Fang Wanzhi,

81
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:19,480
you may leave now.

82
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:28,680
Ms. Fang has a brilliant plan.

83
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:30,070
I support it.

84
00:06:30,830 --> 00:06:31,920
I fully support it!

85
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:33,750
As for the high-tech fair,

86
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:35,270
we must participate in it

87
00:06:35,430 --> 00:06:36,870
if we want our company stronger.

88
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:38,680
Mr. Zhang,

89
00:06:39,270 --> 00:06:40,560
last year, you were opposed to it.

90
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:41,950
Saying it wasted money

91
00:06:42,310 --> 00:06:43,240
and time.

92
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:45,360
Did... Did I?

93
00:06:45,870 --> 00:06:46,630
At that time,

94
00:06:46,750 --> 00:06:48,190
there was no one like Ms. Fang

95
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:49,430
to explain this

96
00:06:49,510 --> 00:06:50,800
in a thorough way.

97
00:06:50,950 --> 00:06:51,870
Do you agree with me?

98
00:06:52,310 --> 00:06:52,830
Indeed.

99
00:06:53,750 --> 00:06:54,360
President Yan.

100
00:06:54,510 --> 00:06:55,390
Shall we take a vote?

101
00:06:57,070 --> 00:06:58,270
From their attitude,

102
00:06:58,720 --> 00:06:59,750
do we need to do that?

103
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:01,160
Then it's approved?

104
00:07:19,430 --> 00:07:20,920
Time for a night snack!

105
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,240
Check what I brought you!

106
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:24,310
Wow, delicious food!

107
00:07:25,430 --> 00:07:26,600
Where were you entertaining?

108
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:27,560
So much good food.

109
00:07:28,310 --> 00:07:29,800
I bought these specially for you two.

110
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:30,830
Auntie Wanzhi, sit.

111
00:07:30,830 --> 00:07:32,870
What good news? Tell us.

112
00:07:36,870 --> 00:07:38,310
I got promoted.

113
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:40,560
Treated as a vice president.

114
00:07:40,950 --> 00:07:42,720
My salary went up two levels.

115
00:07:43,270 --> 00:07:43,950
Auntie Wanzhi,

116
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,270
you're amazing!

117
00:07:45,510 --> 00:07:46,560
Oh my gosh.

118
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:47,600
I need to pay for a meal

119
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:48,560
to celebrate it!

120
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:49,510
Don't forget Gao Xiang.

121
00:07:49,950 --> 00:07:51,120
Wait a while.

122
00:07:51,390 --> 00:07:53,000
My company is busy

123
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:54,310
preparing for the high-tech fair.

124
00:07:54,830 --> 00:07:56,360
Yan Ziwei put me in charge of it.

125
00:07:56,750 --> 00:07:57,310
Wait.

126
00:07:58,750 --> 00:07:59,870
Who is Yan Ziwei?

127
00:08:00,270 --> 00:08:01,240
Your president?

128
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:06,000
It's your first time to call him this.

129
00:08:06,390 --> 00:08:08,040
You used to call him

130
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:08,830
President Yan,

131
00:08:08,870 --> 00:08:10,190
or Mr. Yan?

132
00:08:11,870 --> 00:08:13,750
He isn't here now.

133
00:08:14,360 --> 00:08:15,310
President?

134
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,430
How old is he?

135
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,240
Fifty? Or sixty?

136
00:08:19,750 --> 00:08:20,830
About my age.

137
00:08:21,830 --> 00:08:24,040
He looks cold,

138
00:08:24,750 --> 00:08:25,870
but when he's at work,

139
00:08:26,310 --> 00:08:27,240
he's very decisive

140
00:08:27,600 --> 00:08:28,430
and visionary.

141
00:08:29,070 --> 00:08:29,800
Fang Wanzhi.

142
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:31,560
You're acting weird.

143
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:32,720
What?

144
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:34,270
Yan Ziwei.

145
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:37,840
Don't talk nonsense.

146
00:08:38,750 --> 00:08:39,480
Auntie Juan.

147
00:08:39,870 --> 00:08:41,360
What are you talking about?

148
00:08:41,790 --> 00:08:43,080
I don't understand.

149
00:08:44,510 --> 00:08:45,550
It's better that you don't.

150
00:08:45,750 --> 00:08:46,320
Let's eat.

151
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:36,870
Ms. Fang,

152
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:37,750
come with us.

153
00:09:46,150 --> 00:09:47,200
At this high-tech fair,

154
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:47,960
we signed

155
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:49,360
four strategic agreements,

156
00:09:49,550 --> 00:09:50,030
and would earn

157
00:09:50,030 --> 00:09:51,440
more than 100 million yuan.

158
00:09:51,910 --> 00:09:52,510
Thank you.

159
00:09:56,750 --> 00:09:58,240
You deserve the most credit.

160
00:09:59,030 --> 00:09:59,840
It's my duty.

161
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:01,600
Later, someone in finance

162
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:02,630
will find you for signatures.

163
00:10:03,080 --> 00:10:03,720
Congratulations.

164
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:04,840
You're getting a bonus!

165
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:06,550
Ms. Yao.

166
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:08,390
I don't want

167
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:10,030
this bonus.

168
00:10:11,030 --> 00:10:12,030
I caused a huge loss

169
00:10:12,030 --> 00:10:13,480
for our company before.

170
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:17,630
President Yan approved the bonus.

171
00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:18,870
But...

172
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:20,440
Don't turn down his kindness.

173
00:10:24,270 --> 00:10:24,840
Thank you.

174
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:26,960
Many executives in Hongtu

175
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:27,720
are from Hong Kong, China.

176
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:29,270
When they work in Shenzhen,

177
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:31,120
the company pays for their apartments.

178
00:10:31,630 --> 00:10:33,360
Now you've reached the level.

179
00:10:36,030 --> 00:10:37,080
The apartment for you.

180
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:39,000
No, thanks.

181
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:40,150
I have a place to live.

182
00:10:40,390 --> 00:10:41,750
This is a company benefit.

183
00:10:42,150 --> 00:10:43,440
I picked it specially.

184
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:44,720
It's quite good.

185
00:10:45,510 --> 00:10:47,150
President Yan is also in this community.

186
00:10:47,750 --> 00:10:49,200
If you move here, it'll be closer

187
00:10:49,600 --> 00:10:50,600
and convenient to work.

188
00:10:51,150 --> 00:10:51,960
No need.

189
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:53,440
Living where I am now

190
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:54,720
won't affect my work.

191
00:10:55,440 --> 00:10:55,960
Alright.

192
00:10:56,390 --> 00:10:57,200
I'll keep it first.

193
00:10:57,510 --> 00:10:58,600
Find me if you need it.

194
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:00,550
Thank you, Ms. Yao.

195
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:04,150
You're all awake.

196
00:11:04,750 --> 00:11:05,840
My treat tonight

197
00:11:05,960 --> 00:11:07,240
to celebrate your promotion.

198
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:08,550
I've already invited Gao Xiang.

199
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:09,550
Nice!

200
00:11:09,670 --> 00:11:10,840
I don't have class tonight.

201
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:12,240
Even so, you still can't join us.

202
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:13,240
Go home and sleep.

203
00:11:13,670 --> 00:11:15,320
You work so long every day,

204
00:11:15,390 --> 00:11:16,750
so you can't lack sleep.

205
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:18,550
Fine, follow Wanzhi's words.

206
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:19,510
I'll pack the food.

207
00:11:20,320 --> 00:11:20,870
Alright.

208
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:22,000
I gotta go.

209
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:23,150
Take care.

210
00:11:37,630 --> 00:11:38,440
Why do you always

211
00:11:38,440 --> 00:11:39,510
invite Gao Xiang?

212
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:40,720
Mr. Gao has been

213
00:11:40,750 --> 00:11:42,030
asking about you.

214
00:11:42,150 --> 00:11:43,360
Right after the high-tech fair,

215
00:11:43,390 --> 00:11:44,150
he asked me

216
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:45,120
if you have time

217
00:11:45,120 --> 00:11:45,960
for dinner together.

218
00:11:46,960 --> 00:11:47,550
Why didn't he

219
00:11:47,600 --> 00:11:48,600
ask me himself?

220
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:50,200
I see him every night

221
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:51,440
at evening school.

222
00:11:52,150 --> 00:11:53,240
How's he doing lately?

223
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:54,510
Great!

224
00:11:55,150 --> 00:11:56,030
Let me tell you.

225
00:11:56,480 --> 00:11:57,550
Mr. Gao

226
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:59,030
is really a good teacher.

227
00:11:59,390 --> 00:12:00,630
Simple and vivid.

228
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:02,510
Always making us laugh.

229
00:12:02,600 --> 00:12:03,790
Nobody dozes off in his class.

230
00:12:03,870 --> 00:12:04,910
Sometimes no seats are available,

231
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:06,240
so people stand.

232
00:12:06,670 --> 00:12:07,600
And the point is

233
00:12:08,240 --> 00:12:09,320
most are girls.

234
00:12:12,510 --> 00:12:13,270
Why are you looking

235
00:12:13,270 --> 00:12:13,790
at me?

236
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:15,150
Nothing to do with me.

237
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:22,200
This beef is delicious.

238
00:12:22,720 --> 00:12:23,030
Thanks.

239
00:12:23,030 --> 00:12:23,750
Fang Wanzhi.

240
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:25,200
A gift for you.

241
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:26,030
What's this?

242
00:12:26,030 --> 00:12:26,600
Take a look.

243
00:12:30,630 --> 00:12:31,670
I took it by myself.

244
00:12:31,870 --> 00:12:32,320
How is it?

245
00:12:32,550 --> 00:12:33,600
You're at the scene?

246
00:12:34,790 --> 00:12:35,750
Seeing you running around,

247
00:12:35,870 --> 00:12:36,720
I didn't disturb you.

248
00:12:37,790 --> 00:12:38,550
Congratulations!

249
00:12:38,870 --> 00:12:39,600
Taking a group photo

250
00:12:39,630 --> 00:12:40,790
at the signing ceremony

251
00:12:40,790 --> 00:12:41,630
fully shows

252
00:12:41,750 --> 00:12:43,270
you're indeed important at Hongtu.

253
00:12:44,030 --> 00:12:45,440
I was just doing support.

254
00:12:45,720 --> 00:12:46,240
No...

255
00:12:47,200 --> 00:12:48,000
I noticed

256
00:12:48,870 --> 00:12:49,910
you were in charge of

257
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:50,840
the entire booth

258
00:12:50,870 --> 00:12:51,840
and business negotiations.

259
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:53,200
How did you know that?

260
00:12:53,390 --> 00:12:54,360
I followed you.

261
00:12:54,550 --> 00:12:54,840
I...

262
00:12:56,440 --> 00:12:57,360
Just kidding.

263
00:12:57,870 --> 00:12:58,600
I am

264
00:12:58,960 --> 00:12:59,670
a special reporter

265
00:12:59,750 --> 00:13:00,870
for the high-tech fair.

266
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:02,000
Providing news reports

267
00:13:02,120 --> 00:13:03,000
for major newspapers.

268
00:13:03,750 --> 00:13:04,200
Oh!

269
00:13:04,600 --> 00:13:05,630
Another gift for you.

270
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:07,120
Another one?

271
00:13:08,120 --> 00:13:08,960
What is it? Show me.

272
00:13:12,910 --> 00:13:14,120
Afraid of disturbing you,

273
00:13:14,750 --> 00:13:15,870
I, the on-site reporter,

274
00:13:15,870 --> 00:13:16,870
just served you quietly

275
00:13:16,870 --> 00:13:18,440
nearby.

276
00:13:19,080 --> 00:13:20,750
Gao Xiang, you're amazing!

277
00:13:20,840 --> 00:13:21,510
Wanzhi was nice

278
00:13:21,510 --> 00:13:22,270
in this photo.

279
00:13:22,270 --> 00:13:23,000
Right?

280
00:13:23,120 --> 00:13:24,550
Did you ask for my permission?

281
00:13:24,720 --> 00:13:25,790
Everybody. Cheers!

282
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:28,720
Cheers!

283
00:13:28,750 --> 00:13:29,390
Thank you.

284
00:13:29,390 --> 00:13:30,240
Enjoy!

285
00:13:34,150 --> 00:13:35,030
Gao Xiang has always

286
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:36,240
been caring about you

287
00:13:36,320 --> 00:13:37,440
for all these years.

288
00:13:37,870 --> 00:13:39,320
Hurry up and marry him.

289
00:13:40,510 --> 00:13:41,960
Marry him?

290
00:13:42,670 --> 00:13:44,150
I don't feel that way about him.

291
00:13:45,550 --> 00:13:46,960
And he never even chased me.

292
00:13:47,360 --> 00:13:48,150
Not once.

293
00:13:48,960 --> 00:13:50,960
He really likes you.

294
00:13:51,550 --> 00:13:52,670
He treats you differently

295
00:13:52,720 --> 00:13:53,440
from other girls.

296
00:13:55,870 --> 00:13:56,440
Look.

297
00:13:58,240 --> 00:13:58,630
Here.

298
00:13:59,120 --> 00:13:59,600
Toast

299
00:13:59,720 --> 00:14:00,240
to you.

300
00:14:00,240 --> 00:14:01,360
Cheers!

301
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:03,240
Where is the difference?

302
00:14:05,360 --> 00:14:06,790
You don't have a thing for Yan Ziwei,

303
00:14:06,790 --> 00:14:07,910
do you?

304
00:14:13,270 --> 00:14:14,550
Look at the cook there.

305
00:14:17,200 --> 00:14:17,870
Zhu?

306
00:14:30,630 --> 00:14:31,270
Why didn't you

307
00:14:31,320 --> 00:14:32,550
tell us you came to Shenzhen?

308
00:14:35,030 --> 00:14:36,480
I was afraid you'd tip her off.

309
00:14:36,870 --> 00:14:38,000
You mean Qian?

310
00:14:38,840 --> 00:14:40,080
She doesn't know you're here?

311
00:14:40,550 --> 00:14:41,550
Never, ever tell her.

312
00:14:43,870 --> 00:14:45,240
Didn't you make up

313
00:14:45,270 --> 00:14:46,870
last time you left?

314
00:14:47,200 --> 00:14:48,270
It didn't last half a year.

315
00:14:49,360 --> 00:14:51,120
Her pager kept ringing all day.

316
00:14:51,440 --> 00:14:52,510
Then she ran to call back

317
00:14:52,600 --> 00:14:53,790
at the village committee.

318
00:14:54,270 --> 00:14:55,390
She laughed flirtatiously.

319
00:14:55,910 --> 00:14:57,270
The whole village laughed at me.

320
00:14:58,150 --> 00:14:59,670
My dad told me to discipline her,

321
00:15:00,480 --> 00:15:01,240
but instead,

322
00:15:01,670 --> 00:15:02,840
she lost her temper first.

323
00:15:03,120 --> 00:15:04,120
Scratched my face

324
00:15:04,150 --> 00:15:05,080
and neck.

325
00:15:05,630 --> 00:15:06,670
I slapped her.

326
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:09,080
Then she ran away.

327
00:15:09,790 --> 00:15:10,910
Why not come for her sooner?

328
00:15:11,080 --> 00:15:12,120
I tried.

329
00:15:13,080 --> 00:15:14,670
I've been here five times.

330
00:15:15,150 --> 00:15:16,630
And I have Dahu.

331
00:15:18,910 --> 00:15:20,510
If we both left him,

332
00:15:22,670 --> 00:15:24,200
how miserable he would be!

333
00:15:26,910 --> 00:15:28,030
Now my kid's older,

334
00:15:28,440 --> 00:15:29,670
so I made up my mind.

335
00:15:31,550 --> 00:15:32,790
Either I take her back,

336
00:15:34,630 --> 00:15:35,750
or I'll kill her.

337
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:36,870
That's nonsense!

338
00:15:41,000 --> 00:15:42,600
Someone saw her at this food stall.

339
00:15:43,270 --> 00:15:44,360
So I got a job here

340
00:15:45,320 --> 00:15:46,480
to wait for her.

341
00:15:47,390 --> 00:15:48,600
If I run into her...

342
00:15:49,000 --> 00:15:49,670
Zhu.

343
00:15:50,550 --> 00:15:51,360
Do you remember

344
00:15:51,360 --> 00:15:52,440
what I told you back then?

345
00:15:53,320 --> 00:15:54,910
Violence can't solve any problems.

346
00:15:57,870 --> 00:15:59,030
Maybe I can find her.

347
00:15:59,790 --> 00:16:00,910
But you have to promise me

348
00:16:01,360 --> 00:16:02,080
when you meet her,

349
00:16:02,320 --> 00:16:03,790
talk to her calmly.

350
00:16:08,360 --> 00:16:09,030
Wanzhi.

351
00:16:10,200 --> 00:16:11,670
If you can help me find Qian

352
00:16:12,510 --> 00:16:13,630
and persuade her to come back,

353
00:16:14,080 --> 00:16:14,840
you'll be the savior

354
00:16:15,390 --> 00:16:17,000
of my whole family.

355
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:17,910
- Zhu!
- Please!

356
00:16:17,910 --> 00:16:18,960
What are you doing?

357
00:16:21,870 --> 00:16:22,670
I'll try my best.

358
00:16:29,790 --> 00:16:30,360
Come in.

359
00:16:32,360 --> 00:16:33,000
Ms. Yao.

360
00:16:33,600 --> 00:16:35,630
I've thought it over these days.

361
00:16:35,910 --> 00:16:37,390
The company was considerate.

362
00:16:38,120 --> 00:16:39,510
Living closer to President Yan

363
00:16:39,630 --> 00:16:41,240
does make my work easier.

364
00:16:44,120 --> 00:16:45,670
That's the spirit.

365
00:16:46,600 --> 00:16:47,960
Luckily, I didn't give that house

366
00:16:48,000 --> 00:16:48,720
to others.

367
00:16:50,150 --> 00:16:51,200
I've visited the house.

368
00:16:51,360 --> 00:16:52,750
Two bedrooms. Very spacious.

369
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:54,440
The community is nice, too.

370
00:16:55,000 --> 00:16:56,360
Move in with me.

371
00:16:56,600 --> 00:16:58,000
We'll take the larger room.

372
00:16:58,550 --> 00:16:59,480
Zhao Jun takes the other.

373
00:16:59,790 --> 00:17:01,080
I'm not going with you.

374
00:17:01,360 --> 00:17:02,910
It's too far from the warehouse.

375
00:17:03,240 --> 00:17:05,030
Although the house is nicer,

376
00:17:05,030 --> 00:17:06,200
what about the commute?

377
00:17:06,240 --> 00:17:06,750
Taxi?

378
00:17:06,880 --> 00:17:07,830
Costs too much.

379
00:17:08,200 --> 00:17:09,000
Don't forget

380
00:17:09,110 --> 00:17:09,960
I'm your employee.

381
00:17:09,960 --> 00:17:11,400
You have to calculate profits.

382
00:17:11,590 --> 00:17:13,550
Profits can be a little less.

383
00:17:13,790 --> 00:17:15,000
But we're besties.

384
00:17:15,270 --> 00:17:16,350
Come on.

385
00:17:16,590 --> 00:17:17,550
We are still besties

386
00:17:17,640 --> 00:17:18,550
even if

387
00:17:18,550 --> 00:17:19,750
we don't live together.

388
00:17:23,350 --> 00:17:24,110
I'm not going either.

389
00:17:24,790 --> 00:17:25,400
Auntie Juan.

390
00:17:25,750 --> 00:17:26,640
If she moves out,

391
00:17:26,790 --> 00:17:27,440
I can pay

392
00:17:27,510 --> 00:17:28,440
more rent here.

393
00:17:28,590 --> 00:17:29,270
Wait. Zhao Jun.

394
00:17:29,350 --> 00:17:30,590
Why are you

395
00:17:30,680 --> 00:17:31,920
still so formal?

396
00:17:32,310 --> 00:17:34,480
She insists on paying every month

397
00:17:34,640 --> 00:17:36,030
even though I refuse.

398
00:17:36,310 --> 00:17:37,640
Zhao Jun, just come with me.

399
00:17:37,830 --> 00:17:39,000
It's closer to where you work.

400
00:17:39,070 --> 00:17:40,480
You can sleep half an hour longer.

401
00:17:40,720 --> 00:17:41,310
Auntie Wanzhi,

402
00:17:41,550 --> 00:17:43,030
I'm used to living here.

403
00:17:43,830 --> 00:17:44,480
It's far,

404
00:17:44,680 --> 00:17:45,960
but only one transfer.

405
00:17:46,070 --> 00:17:46,720
It's convenient.

406
00:17:46,920 --> 00:17:48,240
If Auntie Juan's on a business trip,

407
00:17:48,480 --> 00:17:49,920
I can help feed Little Friend.

408
00:17:52,070 --> 00:17:53,400
Then bring it, too.

409
00:17:53,640 --> 00:17:54,680
Absolutely not.

410
00:17:55,000 --> 00:17:56,110
It needs to be with me.

411
00:17:57,590 --> 00:17:58,440
So none of you

412
00:17:58,480 --> 00:17:59,590
want to move?

413
00:18:00,000 --> 00:18:02,350
It's fine to move there alone.

414
00:18:02,640 --> 00:18:04,110
Convenient for dating.

415
00:18:04,550 --> 00:18:05,640
What are you talking about?

416
00:18:05,720 --> 00:18:06,640
No.

417
00:18:06,880 --> 00:18:07,510
I just...

418
00:18:08,270 --> 00:18:09,270
Keep drinking!

419
00:18:09,590 --> 00:18:10,920
Depth charge!

420
00:18:12,000 --> 00:18:13,200
Slow down! Be careful.

421
00:18:13,240 --> 00:18:14,070
We're home...

422
00:18:14,070 --> 00:18:14,510
You can

423
00:18:14,510 --> 00:18:15,240
try our coffee.

424
00:18:15,350 --> 00:18:16,400
Our coffee is good.

425
00:18:19,270 --> 00:18:19,920
Enjoy yourself.

426
00:18:20,590 --> 00:18:21,350
Hello, Ms. Fang.

427
00:18:21,480 --> 00:18:22,270
Hello, manager.

428
00:18:23,270 --> 00:18:24,160
Mr. Yan told me

429
00:18:24,160 --> 00:18:25,200
you'd moved here.

430
00:18:25,310 --> 00:18:26,550
Ask me if you need help.

431
00:18:26,680 --> 00:18:27,310
Thanks.

432
00:18:28,510 --> 00:18:29,070
Manager?

433
00:18:30,510 --> 00:18:31,750
Do you remember the person

434
00:18:31,750 --> 00:18:33,070
I asked about?

435
00:18:33,400 --> 00:18:34,000
Who?

436
00:18:34,440 --> 00:18:35,550
One night,

437
00:18:35,590 --> 00:18:36,750
a man and a woman,

438
00:18:36,830 --> 00:18:37,790
who were both drunk,

439
00:18:37,920 --> 00:18:38,590
were walking inside.

440
00:18:38,640 --> 00:18:39,590
I chased

441
00:18:39,640 --> 00:18:40,310
and asked you...

442
00:18:40,310 --> 00:18:41,350
Sorry, Ms. Fang.

443
00:18:42,070 --> 00:18:43,550
I don't remember that at all.

444
00:18:49,680 --> 00:18:50,200
Slow down.

445
00:18:51,480 --> 00:18:52,400
Come on, keep drinking.

446
00:18:54,000 --> 00:18:55,270
I'm fearless.

447
00:18:56,640 --> 00:18:59,000
I want a depth charge.

448
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:01,480
I...

449
00:19:01,590 --> 00:19:02,750
I am not drunk.

450
00:19:04,000 --> 00:19:04,550
Manager.

451
00:19:07,440 --> 00:19:08,030
Ms. Fang.

452
00:19:08,240 --> 00:19:08,920
You're still here?

453
00:19:09,750 --> 00:19:11,110
Want something to drink?

454
00:19:11,510 --> 00:19:11,960
No need.

455
00:19:12,720 --> 00:19:14,110
The club has rooms?

456
00:19:15,510 --> 00:19:16,960
We have a few VIP rooms,

457
00:19:17,160 --> 00:19:18,640
reserved yearly for VIP members.

458
00:19:19,400 --> 00:19:20,640
If Mr. Yan needs them,

459
00:19:20,790 --> 00:19:21,960
you can book in advance.

460
00:19:22,110 --> 00:19:23,680
You're given the priority.

461
00:19:25,640 --> 00:19:27,110
Anything else?

462
00:19:31,350 --> 00:19:33,240
The surname of that sir just now?

463
00:19:35,790 --> 00:19:36,750
Sorry, Ms. Fang.

464
00:19:37,400 --> 00:19:38,110
I don't know

465
00:19:38,160 --> 00:19:39,240
who you're talking about.

466
00:19:40,110 --> 00:19:40,960
I'm busy. I gotta go.

467
00:20:36,790 --> 00:20:37,440
Madam.

468
00:20:37,920 --> 00:20:38,640
Hello.

469
00:20:39,590 --> 00:20:40,510
Good morning.

470
00:20:40,640 --> 00:20:41,270
Good morning.

471
00:20:41,590 --> 00:20:42,960
How long have you worked here?

472
00:20:43,400 --> 00:20:44,200
Four years.

473
00:20:44,550 --> 00:20:45,350
So you know

474
00:20:45,350 --> 00:20:46,350
all the residents here?

475
00:20:47,110 --> 00:20:48,510
Of course not.

476
00:20:48,640 --> 00:20:50,310
The community is too huge.

477
00:20:50,400 --> 00:20:51,000
Villas,

478
00:20:51,200 --> 00:20:52,000
townhouses,

479
00:20:52,440 --> 00:20:53,200
and apartments.

480
00:20:53,680 --> 00:20:55,640
I'm only in charge of this area.

481
00:20:55,920 --> 00:20:57,240
As for the villas,

482
00:20:57,400 --> 00:20:59,240
I'm not even allowed in.

483
00:20:59,480 --> 00:21:00,440
You...

484
00:21:00,880 --> 00:21:01,550
Nothing.

485
00:21:01,590 --> 00:21:02,440
Just wondering.

486
00:21:21,790 --> 00:21:22,400
Morning.

487
00:21:43,270 --> 00:21:44,350
Jogging like this

488
00:21:44,510 --> 00:21:45,680
won't help you exercise.

489
00:21:46,240 --> 00:21:47,480
Hurry in. Keep up.

490
00:22:01,550 --> 00:22:02,880
I can't run anymore.

491
00:22:03,240 --> 00:22:04,270
Mr. Yan, you go ahead.

492
00:22:04,350 --> 00:22:05,480
Don't let me disturb you.

493
00:22:06,270 --> 00:22:07,830
There's no shortcut to exercise.

494
00:22:07,960 --> 00:22:09,030
Only persistence works.

495
00:22:09,480 --> 00:22:10,030
Alright.

496
00:22:35,720 --> 00:22:36,440
This time,

497
00:22:36,440 --> 00:22:37,830
didn't you run too fast?

498
00:22:38,400 --> 00:22:40,030
That would hurt you.

499
00:22:40,310 --> 00:22:41,310
Take it slow.

500
00:22:57,070 --> 00:22:57,590
Juan.

501
00:22:58,200 --> 00:22:58,750
What's up?

502
00:23:00,200 --> 00:23:01,510
Tomorrow is the weekend.

503
00:23:01,550 --> 00:23:02,350
No overtime, right?

504
00:23:02,590 --> 00:23:03,510
Come back tonight.

505
00:23:03,550 --> 00:23:04,720
I'll make dumplings for you.

506
00:23:05,480 --> 00:23:06,110
I really want

507
00:23:06,160 --> 00:23:07,160
your dumplings,

508
00:23:07,510 --> 00:23:09,160
but I still have work to do.

509
00:23:09,480 --> 00:23:10,160
I can't go back.

510
00:23:11,640 --> 00:23:12,200
Wait a minute.

511
00:23:13,680 --> 00:23:14,480
Zhu contacted me,

512
00:23:14,750 --> 00:23:15,920
pressing for Qian's news.

513
00:23:17,480 --> 00:23:18,240
I got it.

514
00:23:19,000 --> 00:23:19,880
Steady him first.

515
00:23:20,030 --> 00:23:20,920
Tell him

516
00:23:21,440 --> 00:23:21,880
it'll be soon.

517
00:23:40,160 --> 00:23:41,000
Mr. Li.

518
00:23:41,960 --> 00:23:42,830
Long time no see.

519
00:23:43,550 --> 00:23:44,920
Madam, you've got the wrong person.

520
00:23:45,240 --> 00:23:46,030
My surname is Xu.

521
00:23:46,790 --> 00:23:47,590
Mr. Xu.

522
00:23:48,200 --> 00:23:49,030
Sorry, bad memory.

523
00:23:49,350 --> 00:23:50,310
Could you tell me

524
00:23:50,350 --> 00:23:51,750
how to contact Hao Qianqian?

525
00:23:53,920 --> 00:23:54,680
I don't know her,

526
00:23:55,070 --> 00:23:56,110
or you.

527
00:23:56,550 --> 00:23:57,750
I'm Qian's friend.

528
00:23:58,110 --> 00:23:59,030
It's urgent.

529
00:23:59,160 --> 00:24:00,510
Please help me.

530
00:24:03,070 --> 00:24:04,640
I said I don't know her.

531
00:24:04,830 --> 00:24:06,200
I'm taking my wife out now.

532
00:24:06,640 --> 00:24:07,640
Don't be unreasonable.

533
00:24:10,070 --> 00:24:10,750
Mrs. Xu.

534
00:24:11,480 --> 00:24:12,270
Good morning.

535
00:24:13,160 --> 00:24:13,880
Good morning.

536
00:24:14,720 --> 00:24:15,510
From your accent,

537
00:24:15,510 --> 00:24:16,550
you're not a local.

538
00:24:17,160 --> 00:24:17,880
Yes.

539
00:24:18,510 --> 00:24:20,000
Every time I run past your house,

540
00:24:20,000 --> 00:24:21,310
I can't help looking.

541
00:24:21,590 --> 00:24:23,240
Your flowers are so beautiful.

542
00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:24,550
Madam,

543
00:24:24,720 --> 00:24:25,640
what's your name?

544
00:24:25,680 --> 00:24:26,400
My surname is Fang.

545
00:24:26,960 --> 00:24:28,790
Ms. Fang, you like flowers too?

546
00:24:29,480 --> 00:24:30,030
Wait here.

547
00:24:30,070 --> 00:24:30,960
I'll cut you some branches.

548
00:24:31,510 --> 00:24:32,270
Thank you.

549
00:24:35,880 --> 00:24:36,680
What are you doing?

550
00:24:38,030 --> 00:24:39,960
Mrs. Xu, you're so kind.

551
00:24:40,200 --> 00:24:40,960
Can I chat with you

552
00:24:40,960 --> 00:24:42,350
when I'm free?

553
00:24:42,720 --> 00:24:43,510
Ms. Fang,

554
00:24:43,640 --> 00:24:45,200
welcome for tea anytime.

555
00:24:46,720 --> 00:24:47,680
If you continue this,

556
00:24:48,000 --> 00:24:48,960
I'll call the security.

557
00:24:49,790 --> 00:24:50,720
If you don't want me

558
00:24:50,750 --> 00:24:51,720
to bother you every day,

559
00:24:52,310 --> 00:24:53,550
tell Hao Qianqian to contact me.

560
00:24:57,750 --> 00:24:58,680
Ms. Fang,

561
00:24:58,680 --> 00:25:00,000
I arranged them casually.

562
00:25:00,000 --> 00:25:01,310
Arrange them carefully at home.

563
00:25:01,310 --> 00:25:02,110
Okay, thanks.

564
00:25:02,110 --> 00:25:03,070
They're so lovely.

565
00:25:03,830 --> 00:25:05,200
I won't bother you anymore.

566
00:25:05,750 --> 00:25:06,750
Alright, let's go.

567
00:25:07,070 --> 00:25:08,200
Remember to come for tea!

568
00:25:08,310 --> 00:25:08,880
Bye bye.

569
00:25:08,880 --> 00:25:09,440
Bye.

570
00:25:20,790 --> 00:25:21,310
Hello?

571
00:25:24,110 --> 00:25:24,590
Hold on.

572
00:25:27,750 --> 00:25:28,510
Hao Qianqian.

573
00:25:29,400 --> 00:25:31,160
3 p.m. this Sunday.

574
00:25:31,350 --> 00:25:32,790
At your old house.

575
00:25:33,350 --> 00:25:35,310
Wanzhi, why the rush?

576
00:25:35,550 --> 00:25:36,200
I have to check

577
00:25:36,200 --> 00:25:37,400
if I have appointments.

578
00:25:37,440 --> 00:25:38,550
Cancel them.

579
00:25:38,830 --> 00:25:40,480
If you don't come, you'll regret it.

580
00:25:53,070 --> 00:25:54,680
Wanzhi.

581
00:25:54,920 --> 00:25:56,070
Zhi.

582
00:25:56,270 --> 00:25:57,480
I missed you so much.

583
00:25:57,920 --> 00:25:59,350
Has it been three years?

584
00:25:59,510 --> 00:26:00,750
Be serious.

585
00:26:00,960 --> 00:26:01,790
Didn't we meet

586
00:26:01,880 --> 00:26:02,880
on my birthday?

587
00:26:03,750 --> 00:26:04,510
Hao Qianqian.

588
00:26:04,880 --> 00:26:06,270
Your singing is

589
00:26:06,350 --> 00:26:07,750
much worse than before.

590
00:26:08,240 --> 00:26:08,960
In these years,

591
00:26:09,000 --> 00:26:10,200
drinking has ruined your voice.

592
00:26:11,960 --> 00:26:13,440
You're indeed my good friend.

593
00:26:15,310 --> 00:26:16,510
Not saving my face

594
00:26:16,510 --> 00:26:17,480
at all.

595
00:26:18,440 --> 00:26:18,960
However,

596
00:26:19,110 --> 00:26:21,440
I know you care about me the most.

597
00:26:21,790 --> 00:26:22,480
Deal.

598
00:26:22,480 --> 00:26:23,240
Sunday.

599
00:26:23,480 --> 00:26:24,920
What do you and Juan want to eat?

600
00:26:25,070 --> 00:26:26,240
Alaskan king crab?

601
00:26:26,240 --> 00:26:26,750
Lobster?

602
00:26:27,070 --> 00:26:28,550
Got it. We...

603
00:26:32,680 --> 00:26:33,310
Fang Wanzhi.

604
00:26:35,480 --> 00:26:36,590
Why are you here?

605
00:26:38,200 --> 00:26:39,510
Just passing by.

606
00:26:40,310 --> 00:26:41,750
I don't buy it, Gao Xiang.

607
00:26:42,830 --> 00:26:43,510
What's up?

608
00:26:43,790 --> 00:26:44,200
I...

609
00:26:44,270 --> 00:26:45,310
I've been consulting

610
00:26:45,310 --> 00:26:46,720
for my student's company.

611
00:26:46,960 --> 00:26:48,000
At a meeting this afternoon,

612
00:26:48,030 --> 00:26:49,550
I met a man, also from Yu County.

613
00:26:49,790 --> 00:26:51,200
He is excellent,

614
00:26:51,480 --> 00:26:52,350
very capable.

615
00:26:52,440 --> 00:26:54,310
A senior executive at a global company.

616
00:26:54,680 --> 00:26:55,160
Therefore,

617
00:26:55,240 --> 00:26:56,030
I invited him

618
00:26:56,110 --> 00:26:56,750
for tea

619
00:26:57,070 --> 00:26:57,720
on Sunday.

620
00:26:57,920 --> 00:26:58,350
3 p.m.

621
00:26:58,440 --> 00:26:59,000
I'll pick you up.

622
00:26:59,000 --> 00:26:59,440
Wait,

623
00:26:59,680 --> 00:27:01,200
you arranged it without asking me?

624
00:27:01,350 --> 00:27:02,960
You're from the same county!

625
00:27:04,000 --> 00:27:04,880
I'm busy that day.

626
00:27:05,000 --> 00:27:06,030
I've had an appointment.

627
00:27:07,550 --> 00:27:08,920
Where? Maybe we can join you.

628
00:27:09,070 --> 00:27:09,920
I'll bring him over.

629
00:27:10,070 --> 00:27:11,070
This man is really nice.

630
00:27:11,110 --> 00:27:11,720
No airs at all.

631
00:27:11,720 --> 00:27:12,270
Gao Xiang.

632
00:27:12,680 --> 00:27:14,110
I have something important on Sunday.

633
00:27:14,350 --> 00:27:15,160
Cancel it for me.

634
00:27:16,830 --> 00:27:17,680
And please don't

635
00:27:17,680 --> 00:27:18,310
do that again.

636
00:27:18,550 --> 00:27:19,070
I'm leaving.

637
00:27:40,000 --> 00:27:40,880
Qian is here.

638
00:27:42,110 --> 00:27:42,920
You promised me.

639
00:27:43,400 --> 00:27:44,480
Talk calmly.

640
00:28:00,240 --> 00:28:02,110
Finally missed me.

641
00:28:02,880 --> 00:28:03,830
See what I bought.

642
00:28:11,480 --> 00:28:12,200
Where are you going?

643
00:28:12,750 --> 00:28:13,310
Liu Zhu!

644
00:28:21,480 --> 00:28:22,240
Li Juan.

645
00:28:23,350 --> 00:28:24,590
Fang Wanzhi.

646
00:28:26,680 --> 00:28:27,830
I thought you were

647
00:28:27,960 --> 00:28:29,590
my best friends.

648
00:28:33,350 --> 00:28:34,750
This is how you betray me?

649
00:28:34,830 --> 00:28:35,240
Right?

650
00:28:35,310 --> 00:28:36,510
No one betrayed you.

651
00:28:36,920 --> 00:28:37,680
We mean well.

652
00:28:37,750 --> 00:28:38,400
Well?

653
00:28:38,960 --> 00:28:40,680
I managed to escape.

654
00:28:41,310 --> 00:28:42,920
And you're pushing me
back into the fire.

655
00:28:43,000 --> 00:28:43,920
Meaning well?

656
00:28:46,030 --> 00:28:46,680
Qian.

657
00:28:48,160 --> 00:28:49,000
Go home with me.

658
00:28:49,750 --> 00:28:50,680
Dahu misses you.

659
00:28:51,310 --> 00:28:52,790
He wakes up crying in his dreams.

660
00:28:53,000 --> 00:28:54,240
None of your business. Get out!

661
00:28:56,640 --> 00:28:57,790
I'll talk with them first.

662
00:28:57,960 --> 00:28:59,030
We have nothing to say.

663
00:28:59,480 --> 00:29:00,000
Zhu,

664
00:29:00,720 --> 00:29:01,750
we found your wife back.

665
00:29:02,110 --> 00:29:03,480
Solve your family business.

666
00:29:03,590 --> 00:29:04,310
Wanzhi, let's go.

667
00:29:05,070 --> 00:29:06,110
Liu Zhu, get out.

668
00:29:06,200 --> 00:29:07,240
Didn't you hear me?

669
00:29:35,550 --> 00:29:36,200
What to drink?

670
00:29:39,270 --> 00:29:41,110
I brought red wine and liquor.

671
00:29:42,110 --> 00:29:43,030
I've quit beer.

672
00:29:44,680 --> 00:29:46,550
Who are you putting on airs for?

673
00:29:47,920 --> 00:29:49,200
We shared the same bed

674
00:29:49,270 --> 00:29:50,310
and table.

675
00:29:50,400 --> 00:29:51,590
I know who you are.

676
00:29:53,750 --> 00:29:55,110
I know it's good wine,

677
00:29:56,240 --> 00:29:57,270
but nobody cares.

678
00:29:58,590 --> 00:29:59,240
Hao Qianqian,

679
00:30:01,240 --> 00:30:02,400
one day,

680
00:30:04,070 --> 00:30:06,110
when you get by,

681
00:30:07,000 --> 00:30:07,790
and I,

682
00:30:08,030 --> 00:30:09,160
almost as poor

683
00:30:09,400 --> 00:30:10,160
as a church mouse,

684
00:30:10,270 --> 00:30:11,310
have few foods,

685
00:30:13,200 --> 00:30:14,270
I'll cook you porridge

686
00:30:16,160 --> 00:30:17,880
if I have a handful of rice.

687
00:30:22,790 --> 00:30:24,680
I love hearing you talk like this.

688
00:30:25,160 --> 00:30:26,160
Indeed.

689
00:30:28,160 --> 00:30:28,830
I know

690
00:30:28,880 --> 00:30:30,000
a loyal person like you

691
00:30:30,830 --> 00:30:31,440
would never

692
00:30:31,480 --> 00:30:33,030
betray me like Fang Wanzhi.

693
00:30:33,110 --> 00:30:34,160
What did Wanzhi do?

694
00:30:35,000 --> 00:30:36,160
Is "betray" the right word

695
00:30:36,200 --> 00:30:37,000
for her?

696
00:30:39,310 --> 00:30:42,270
Zhu has come to Shenzhen five times.

697
00:30:42,550 --> 00:30:43,830
Staying here another half a year,

698
00:30:43,920 --> 00:30:45,240
he has asked everywhere about you.

699
00:30:45,550 --> 00:30:46,270
Without Wanzhi,

700
00:30:46,310 --> 00:30:47,440
you might have been attacked

701
00:30:47,590 --> 00:30:49,070
in the dark one day

702
00:30:49,160 --> 00:30:50,550
and never know who did this.

703
00:30:50,550 --> 00:30:51,960
How couldn't I know?

704
00:30:52,400 --> 00:30:54,350
He refuses to divorce me.

705
00:30:54,880 --> 00:30:56,590
You know me well.

706
00:30:56,640 --> 00:30:57,960
I keep my mouth shut,

707
00:30:58,680 --> 00:31:01,000
but I'm terrified actually.

708
00:31:01,830 --> 00:31:02,830
His family never

709
00:31:02,830 --> 00:31:03,790
treated me like a person.

710
00:31:04,070 --> 00:31:05,110
After my first child,

711
00:31:05,200 --> 00:31:06,590
they wanted a second.

712
00:31:06,720 --> 00:31:08,110
I called my friend

713
00:31:08,270 --> 00:31:09,640
a little too long,

714
00:31:09,680 --> 00:31:10,440
and his whole family

715
00:31:10,480 --> 00:31:11,680
rolled their eyes.

716
00:31:16,240 --> 00:31:18,680
And they egged Zhu on to hit me.

717
00:31:21,070 --> 00:31:22,510
Is this a life for humans?

718
00:31:23,550 --> 00:31:25,240
Why didn't you talk to him

719
00:31:25,440 --> 00:31:26,720
to move to Shenzhen with Dahu?

720
00:31:27,070 --> 00:31:28,110
Talking to someone

721
00:31:28,110 --> 00:31:29,070
who beats me?

722
00:31:31,030 --> 00:31:32,960
Besides, I did tell him.

723
00:31:33,880 --> 00:31:34,750
He refused.

724
00:31:35,590 --> 00:31:36,310
He said

725
00:31:36,960 --> 00:31:38,720
they built five tile houses,

726
00:31:39,200 --> 00:31:40,960
so I had to stay with him

727
00:31:41,030 --> 00:31:41,920
in his hometown

728
00:31:42,000 --> 00:31:44,480
and care for his parents
until they die.

729
00:31:45,440 --> 00:31:47,310
Liu is perfectly healthy.

730
00:31:47,750 --> 00:31:48,240
So,

731
00:31:48,750 --> 00:31:49,720
waiting for 20 years,

732
00:31:49,830 --> 00:31:50,880
30 years?

733
00:31:51,000 --> 00:31:52,310
You're a little heartless.

734
00:31:52,880 --> 00:31:55,200
I wish his family well.

735
00:31:55,590 --> 00:31:57,640
Long life. Many descendants.

736
00:31:57,750 --> 00:31:59,790
But I can't stay!

737
00:32:02,880 --> 00:32:05,550
I've been starving and bullied.

738
00:32:05,790 --> 00:32:07,960
It's uneasy for me to be alive.

739
00:32:09,750 --> 00:32:10,720
Luckily,

740
00:32:11,920 --> 00:32:13,200
God

741
00:32:14,480 --> 00:32:16,640
is somewhat on my side.

742
00:32:19,830 --> 00:32:21,200
I'm not ugly,

743
00:32:21,880 --> 00:32:23,480
can sing a little,

744
00:32:24,960 --> 00:32:26,550
and men like me.

745
00:32:28,750 --> 00:32:31,110
Why should I be trapped

746
00:32:31,110 --> 00:32:33,510
in that valley forever?

747
00:32:35,510 --> 00:32:37,310
I didn't contact you when I came here

748
00:32:37,960 --> 00:32:39,790
because I was afraid they would catch me

749
00:32:40,070 --> 00:32:40,920
and get you involved.

750
00:32:42,960 --> 00:32:44,510
When I ran away,

751
00:32:44,880 --> 00:32:45,880
my wallet,

752
00:32:46,240 --> 00:32:47,640
pager, and ID card

753
00:32:47,680 --> 00:32:48,720
were all stolen.

754
00:32:50,880 --> 00:32:52,310
To get to Shenzhen,

755
00:32:52,310 --> 00:32:53,920
I suffered so much.

756
00:33:07,880 --> 00:33:09,350
I can't say it.

757
00:33:13,790 --> 00:33:15,240
But it's okay now.

758
00:33:15,680 --> 00:33:17,030
I got my ID card back

759
00:33:17,160 --> 00:33:18,350
and got a driver license.

760
00:33:18,790 --> 00:33:20,680
I have a house and a car.

761
00:33:23,790 --> 00:33:24,920
I can't go back.

762
00:33:26,440 --> 00:33:27,240
Wanzhi.

763
00:33:28,720 --> 00:33:29,400
Juan.

764
00:33:30,830 --> 00:33:32,110
In this world,

765
00:33:34,000 --> 00:33:34,680
I really only

766
00:33:34,680 --> 00:33:36,640
have you as my family.

767
00:33:37,350 --> 00:33:39,240
If you really stand with Zhu

768
00:33:39,240 --> 00:33:41,640
and force me to back,

769
00:33:46,550 --> 00:33:48,880
I'll kill myself in front of you.

770
00:33:49,110 --> 00:33:50,030
Don't say that!

771
00:33:57,110 --> 00:33:58,000
About Liu Zhu...

772
00:33:59,510 --> 00:34:00,790
What's your plan?

773
00:34:01,400 --> 00:34:02,480
Zhu is dead set on this.

774
00:34:03,880 --> 00:34:04,830
I'll send him away.

775
00:34:10,440 --> 00:34:11,840
I knew

776
00:34:13,710 --> 00:34:15,630
you still cared about me.

777
00:34:20,550 --> 00:34:21,630
I, Hao Qianqian,

778
00:34:22,880 --> 00:34:24,760
haven't been living for nothing.

779
00:34:25,070 --> 00:34:26,630
You called me in such a hurry.

780
00:34:26,710 --> 00:34:28,440
I knew he was definitely here.

781
00:34:28,800 --> 00:34:29,710
Don't worry.

782
00:34:30,400 --> 00:34:31,440
I'll solve

783
00:34:33,960 --> 00:34:35,070
my own problems.

784
00:35:06,920 --> 00:35:08,000
How long have you been here?

785
00:35:10,710 --> 00:35:11,590
This time...

786
00:35:12,880 --> 00:35:13,800
Five and a half months.

787
00:35:15,230 --> 00:35:15,960
Must be a hard time.

788
00:35:17,030 --> 00:35:18,590
It's nothing if you come back with me.

789
00:35:20,760 --> 00:35:21,800
Dahu misses you.

790
00:35:23,880 --> 00:35:24,960
I also miss Dahu.

791
00:35:45,800 --> 00:35:46,510
Liu Zhu.

792
00:35:49,070 --> 00:35:50,230
We...

793
00:35:51,480 --> 00:35:52,670
didn't register our marriage.

794
00:35:54,710 --> 00:35:56,320
But my family held a wedding feast.

795
00:35:57,710 --> 00:35:59,510
That meant the marriage.

796
00:35:59,960 --> 00:36:01,590
At that time, your dad said

797
00:36:02,840 --> 00:36:04,480
we'd register after the baby.

798
00:36:05,920 --> 00:36:07,440
If it hadn't been a boy,

799
00:36:07,480 --> 00:36:08,550
what would have happened?

800
00:36:10,590 --> 00:36:12,000
I heard it all.

801
00:36:18,510 --> 00:36:19,230
He never thought

802
00:36:19,230 --> 00:36:20,360
I was qualified, right?

803
00:36:22,710 --> 00:36:23,480
No.

804
00:36:25,960 --> 00:36:28,150
Forget him. I like you anyway.

805
00:36:28,320 --> 00:36:30,440
But I've left for three years.

806
00:36:31,670 --> 00:36:33,320
I haven't been faithful to you.

807
00:36:39,840 --> 00:36:40,670
What?

808
00:36:41,190 --> 00:36:42,150
You're an adult.

809
00:36:42,150 --> 00:36:43,440
Don't you figure it out?

810
00:36:45,230 --> 00:36:46,670
With the five tile houses,

811
00:36:47,760 --> 00:36:48,840
it's easy to get married.

812
00:36:49,630 --> 00:36:50,960
You didn't register your marriage,

813
00:36:51,590 --> 00:36:53,030
so you're still single officially.

814
00:36:53,280 --> 00:36:54,030
It's great.

815
00:36:54,800 --> 00:36:55,960
No!

816
00:36:56,960 --> 00:36:58,880
You have to come back with me.

817
00:36:59,440 --> 00:37:00,550
This isn't your home.

818
00:37:00,550 --> 00:37:01,320
This is Shenzhen.

819
00:37:01,320 --> 00:37:02,190
If you go street on me,

820
00:37:02,190 --> 00:37:04,230
I'll call the police. Believe it or not.

821
00:37:06,880 --> 00:37:08,070
You think I'm uneducated

822
00:37:08,110 --> 00:37:09,190
and illiterate, right?

823
00:37:10,710 --> 00:37:12,230
I've asked a lawyer.

824
00:37:14,070 --> 00:37:15,550
We didn't register our marriage,

825
00:37:15,670 --> 00:37:17,550
so I'd never be your wife.

826
00:37:18,000 --> 00:37:20,110
Your family wants to bully me again?

827
00:37:22,190 --> 00:37:23,110
Daydream.

828
00:37:28,190 --> 00:37:29,670
Once a couple, always a bond.

829
00:37:30,920 --> 00:37:31,880
Dahu is my son.

830
00:37:31,880 --> 00:37:33,440
I have to raise him.

831
00:37:35,710 --> 00:37:36,590
This money

832
00:37:38,480 --> 00:37:39,480
is enough to

833
00:37:39,480 --> 00:37:40,710
grow him up.

834
00:37:41,400 --> 00:37:42,960
Please take good care of him.

835
00:37:44,070 --> 00:37:45,320
Don't let his stepmom bully him.

836
00:37:47,960 --> 00:37:49,280
Money is hard to earn for me.

837
00:37:50,670 --> 00:37:51,840
So I can't give you more.

838
00:37:53,070 --> 00:37:55,030
Say sorry to your dad

839
00:37:55,920 --> 00:37:57,030
and tell him and your mom

840
00:37:58,030 --> 00:37:59,030
to care for the kid.

841
00:38:07,070 --> 00:38:08,960
Let's break up peacefully.

842
00:38:11,230 --> 00:38:11,920
Liu Zhu.

843
00:38:13,190 --> 00:38:14,150
I didn't owe you.

844
00:38:39,360 --> 00:38:40,000
Qian!

845
00:39:08,550 --> 00:39:09,190
Who are you?

846
00:39:09,760 --> 00:39:10,590
Who are you!

847
00:39:12,280 --> 00:39:13,440
I was like you once.

848
00:39:14,190 --> 00:39:15,880
As a result, I spent 3 years in prison.

849
00:39:16,760 --> 00:39:17,960
Do you want to go to jail too?

850
00:39:18,070 --> 00:39:18,670
Zhu.

851
00:39:19,280 --> 00:39:20,030
If you're in prison,

852
00:39:20,030 --> 00:39:20,920
who will care for Dahu?

853
00:39:21,190 --> 00:39:23,070
If you're tough, come at me!

854
00:39:23,190 --> 00:39:24,000
What are you doing?

855
00:39:24,000 --> 00:39:24,550
Stop!

856
00:39:25,280 --> 00:39:25,960
Get off!

857
00:39:25,960 --> 00:39:26,480
Zhu.

858
00:39:27,360 --> 00:39:28,230
Put down the knife.

859
00:39:28,550 --> 00:39:29,550
Or I'll call the police.

860
00:39:31,280 --> 00:39:32,510
Do you hear me?

861
00:39:34,030 --> 00:39:34,710
Wanzhi.

862
00:39:35,840 --> 00:39:37,280
Don't let him call the police,

863
00:39:38,400 --> 00:39:39,320
please.

864
00:39:40,840 --> 00:39:41,510
Gao Xiang.

865
00:39:47,360 --> 00:39:47,880
Zhu.

866
00:39:48,230 --> 00:39:49,800
I won't call the police for now,

867
00:39:50,280 --> 00:39:52,110
but you're doing a crime.

868
00:39:52,510 --> 00:39:53,920
If the victim presses charges,

869
00:39:54,150 --> 00:39:55,510
you'll go to jail at any time.

870
00:39:57,000 --> 00:39:57,920
Sir,

871
00:39:58,510 --> 00:40:00,880
I'm Fang Wanzhi's brother.

872
00:40:02,070 --> 00:40:02,960
Let me talk to you.

873
00:40:15,550 --> 00:40:17,110
I don't want that.

874
00:40:20,800 --> 00:40:21,920
My wife is gone.

875
00:40:22,670 --> 00:40:23,880
I lost my wife.

876
00:40:26,710 --> 00:40:29,880
I lost my wife!

877
00:40:34,440 --> 00:40:35,320
How's your hand?

878
00:40:35,960 --> 00:40:36,670
It's fine.

879
00:40:40,630 --> 00:40:41,230
Mr. Li,

880
00:40:41,840 --> 00:40:42,840
let's see a doctor.

881
00:40:54,920 --> 00:40:55,440
Sir,

882
00:40:56,400 --> 00:40:57,190
you hurt me.

883
00:40:57,510 --> 00:40:58,630
Need to pay the bill, right?

884
00:41:01,030 --> 00:41:02,030
See the doctor with me.

885
00:41:22,840 --> 00:41:23,960
Zhu,

886
00:41:24,070 --> 00:41:25,670
why were you so impulsive?

887
00:41:26,710 --> 00:41:27,670
What if you hurt him

888
00:41:27,760 --> 00:41:28,280
badly?

889
00:41:28,510 --> 00:41:29,800
No thought for the consequences?

890
00:41:30,400 --> 00:41:32,110
My job has me

891
00:41:32,800 --> 00:41:34,000
traveling all over the country.

892
00:41:34,480 --> 00:41:35,070
That makes me

893
00:41:35,110 --> 00:41:36,670
a stranger in my hometown.

894
00:41:38,550 --> 00:41:39,150
I didn't expect

895
00:41:39,230 --> 00:41:40,840
the person Gao Xiang mentioned

896
00:41:41,000 --> 00:41:41,760
was you.

897
00:41:43,000 --> 00:41:44,320
He didn't tell me your name,

898
00:41:44,960 --> 00:41:46,030
but I had an intuition,

899
00:41:46,280 --> 00:41:47,320
it must be you.

900
00:41:57,510 --> 00:41:58,400
Doesn't it hurt you?

901
00:42:02,030 --> 00:42:03,280
If I hadn't grabbed the knife,

902
00:42:03,880 --> 00:42:05,230
I'd be hurting right now.

903
00:42:17,110 --> 00:42:20,960
Gao Xiang... Really a good man.

904
00:42:21,920 --> 00:42:22,760
Does he have a chance

905
00:42:22,800 --> 00:42:23,840
to be your husband?

906
00:42:29,480 --> 00:42:30,760
Seems he still has to work hard.

907
00:42:34,320 --> 00:42:34,840
Wanzhi.

908
00:42:35,920 --> 00:42:36,760
I have a girlfriend.

909
00:42:37,710 --> 00:42:38,440
Really?

910
00:42:39,360 --> 00:42:40,110
Congratulations!

911
00:42:41,510 --> 00:42:43,030
My mom also likes her,

912
00:42:43,320 --> 00:42:44,000
but she says

913
00:42:44,190 --> 00:42:45,320
you need to approve us first.

914
00:42:46,510 --> 00:42:47,480
Where is she?

915
00:42:48,000 --> 00:42:49,190
She came to Shenzhen with me.

916
00:42:49,800 --> 00:42:50,800
I'll treat you to dinner.
